data.meta_description: Very excited to get this series up and going. Some great material available now with more coming. Everyone is welcome! Amelia Morgan #auslaw #corporatelaw…
data.text: Are you seeking a deeper understanding of Australian corporate law? We're excited to introduce our brand new initiative, The Australian Corporate Law Academy. These webinars, led by industry experts, are designed to foster a comprehensive understanding of the core issues facing corporate law today. What’s on offer? We have a range of topics available now: • ESG and its impact on Corporate Law with Timothy Stutt, Amy Henderson and Bianca Marcocci • The Modern Approach to Capital Maintenance with Nicole Pedler and Raul Vellani • Are you executing your documents properly? with Stephen Dobbs • Evolving Australia’s securities framework with Tim McEwen We welcome everyone - our clients, their networks, and the broader legal community - to join us. Watch these sessions and register your interest in future topics via our website: https://lnkd.in/gYKRB3ap Upcoming webinar alert! Our next webinar is on July 2nd where we’ll be exploring Continuous disclosure: The challenges, consequences and the future with Tony Damian and Cameron Hanson Register your interest here:https://lnkd.in/ge2JMzvA Our Partners Amelia Morgan and Tony Damian explain what it’s all about. #law #legaleducation #corporatelaw #legalcareers #webinar
